{"tid":1111321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 一人一個玩鳩街頭健身狗嘅方法","createTime":"2019-04-17T00:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T02:45:58.000Z","uid":39752,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6583f573ebc8026567c1f7f1448066736aae2bde","tid":1111321,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T00:58:17.000Z","msg":"旺角/荃灣/銅鑼灣街頭成日都會有啲健身狗出嚟搭膊頭/攔路/塞卡片等等<br />\n可能大家會屌鳩佢就算，或者會話「你唔好著咁毒出街咪無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n但係就咁屌鳩佢哋或者避開，對佢哋根本不痛不癢，呢個係健身狗到今日仍然生存到嘅原因<br />\n所以想收集一下大家玩鳩健身狗嘅方法，目標係增加健身狗騷擾途人嘅成本，從而減少街頭健身狗嘅數量<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾兩個例子大家參考一下<br />\n一，報警，只要有身體接觸就可以報，輕則班mk俾龜逗下就焗住走，重則遊蕩（故意妨礙他人使用公眾地方，甚至導致他人合理地擔心本身的安全或利益）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二，扮落疊同佢吹水，浪費佢時間，原理就同接到廣告電話扮聽好過直接cut線一樣"},{"pid":"3403e9ce9b77f50a51dc2a62faf4bef2dfe8c687","tid":1111321,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T01:03:38.000Z","msg":"走咗隻健身狗入嚟負皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d028afc24c1cf99ef4ba931815aac048c6d2748","tid":1111321,"uid":104218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"如果有心撚狗<br />\n個日出街唔好袋錢同信用卡<br />\n上釣之後扮哂好有興趣<br />\n玩鳩佢幾個鐘佢先發現碌唔到你卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d02ea8f8395aaf0f0b702f8938ae5595e3b1b7","tid":1111321,"uid":211461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T01:32:52.000Z","msg":"以為你講緊去公園操果隻街頭健身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cf1f0e01489961ae148543c24929b0b8a7c987","tid":1111321,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11d02ea8f8395aaf0f0b702f8938ae5595e3b1b7","tid":1111321,"uid":211461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T01:32:52.000Z","msg":"以為你講緊去公園操果隻街頭健身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:45:58.000Z","msg":"sor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}